{"id":161664,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/澳广-索罗斯称中国错失抑制通胀时机/","date":"2011-06-16T10:00:15Z","modified":"2011-06-16T10:00:15Z","title":"澳广 | 索罗斯称中国错失抑制通胀时机","content":"<div>\n<p>索罗斯称中国错失抑制通胀时机</p>\n<p>彭博通讯社报道，著名投资家索罗斯认为中国错失了对付通胀的时机，可能面对经济硬着陆的风险。.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<p>2011 年 06 月 15 日</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3244490.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/decrease.gif\" alt=\"Decrease\" title=\"Decrease\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3244490.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/standard.gif\" alt=\"Standard\" title=\"Standard\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3244490.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/increase.gif\" alt=\"Increase\" title=\"Increase\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/mailto/mailto-nojs_query.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3244490.htm&#038;presname=/ra\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/email.gif\" alt=\"Email\" title=\"Email\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/printfriendly.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3244490.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/print.gif\" alt=\"Print\" title=\"Print\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3244490.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/favourite.gif\" alt=\"Favourite\" title=\"Favourite\" /></a></p>\n<p>彭博通讯社报道，著名投资家索罗斯认为中国错失了对付通胀的时机，可能面对经济硬着陆的风险。</p>\n<p>报道引述索罗斯的话说，中国已经出现由工资带动的通胀，现时的经济增长正逐渐失去动力。</p>\n<p>至于美国和欧洲，索罗斯说，这两个经济体的银行业未能合理调整资本结构，失衡状况仍未得到解决。</p>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofol